headline: Tracking Lone Pine Capital Portfolio - Q3 2024 Update
summary: Lone Pine Capital's 13F portfolio value increased from $12.33B to $13.41B, with holdings rising from 24 to 29, led by Meta, Amazon, and Vistra Corp. See more.

headline: These 3 Stocks Have Made Warren Buffett the Most Money in 2024. Are They No-Brainer Buys for the New Year?
summary: Warren Buffett once wrote, "The weeds wither away in significance as the flowers bloom."  Using Buffett's analogy, his Berkshire Hathaway garden had lots of blooming flowers in 2024.  Buffett's timing was almost perfect in buying Jefferies.
